    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "That makes sense. When you say hair should be \"conservative and neat,\" can you be a bit more specific? Like, what kind of styles or textures are actually considered professional? I've had a few clients ask if certain natural styles or more traditional/cultural hair ways might be seen as \"distracting\" in those high-pressure environments.",
